      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "As-is sale on a poor-condition vehicle that shows heavy wear inside and out. Expect noticeable cosmetic flaws, tired interior materials, and clear signs of age and hard use, and it should be assumed to need repairs, reconditioning, and general sorting before being relied on as a regular driver. Best suited for a project buyer, parts use, or someone comfortable taking on an older car with obvious needs.",
