    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Affordable fair-condition car with a lot to like for someone seeking solid transportation at a sensible price. It presents respectably overall and should suit a buyer who understands it\u2019s not perfect\u2014expect normal wear, age-related imperfections, and the likelihood of some upkeep or repairs to bring it fully up to your standards. A good opportunity to get into a usable car with room to improve over time.",
      "price": 17900.0,
