      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Value-priced and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle is a practical choice for a budget-minded buyer who needs affordable transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows wear consistent with age and use, but it offers straightforward value for someone comfortable with a vehicle that has cosmetic and mechanical needs. If you\u2019re looking for an inexpensive way to get into a car without overspending, this is a compelling option at an accessible price.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with some life left in it? This car isn\u2019t perfect and is being sold in poor condition, but it could be a great fit for someone who\u2019s handy, needs a budget commuter, or wants a project to tinker with. It\u2019s priced accordingly and offered as an honest, inexpensive option without pretending to be something it\u2019s not. If you want a cheap car with potential, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4200.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with a tough-running powertrain and plenty of usable life left for the next owner. Starts up, moves out well, and has the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it a great candidate for someone who wants an affordable commuter, weekend wrenching project, or dependable spare vehicle. Shows cosmetic wear and age as expected, but the core drivetrain feels honest and serviceable. If you know how to spot value in a well-used machine, this one has real potential without the high entry cost.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap entry point. Honest used car with wear, priced to move. Great for a budget buyer, backup ride, or project. First serious buyer gets it.",
