      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a machine with presence, personality, and plenty of story left to tell. It\u2019s an ideal candidate for someone who sees potential, wants an affordable set of wheels, or enjoys bringing a vehicle back into its next chapter. A budget-friendly way to get into something with real soul.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
